									<div class="dica-item-content">   <div class="content"><p>&#8220;In the past 8 months, we have began using Packlane for large volume orders of 30,000 units at a time. It has been a pleasure working with them as theyâ€™re a full end-to-end solution for our corrugate. They have helped us identify opportunities to produce closer to our warehouse and limit the cost of transport. Perhaps more importantly, their communication is accurate. To date, Packlane has delivered POs on the delivery date agreed upon at order placement.&#8221;</p></div>   <h4 class="item-title">Emma Nelson </h4> <h6 class="item-subtitle">VP Operations, MUDWTR</h6> </div>
